  <description type="morphology">Plants scattered or forming small groups. Leaves 20–50 × 5–13 cm; petiole 10–30 cm; blade yellowing in late summer, veins and veinlets visible in transmitted light, 10–26 cm. Scape 1.5–3 dm. Inflorescences to 1/2 length of proximalmost leaves; bracts lanceolate, 10–20 mm, equaling or longer than pedicel. Flowers: tepal midribs green; pedicel 7–11 mm. 2n = 38.</description>
